name: Antmons
description: Antmons is a casual, lightweight MOBA game with nurturing strategies, teamwork and athleticism. Antmons is more lightweight than Aov, and the 3-minute battle is more leisure and suitable for our target users. Compared to Brawl Stars and Thetan Arena, Antmons has stronger thrill for close fight. Compared with io games, Antmons is more strategic and playable.
